nk "&#272;&#259;ng ky&#769; la&#768;m visa" va&#768; &#273;iê&#768;n thông tin cu&#777;a mi&#768;nh va&#768;o mâ&#771;u form s&#259;&#771;n, g&#417;&#777;i vê&#768; cho chu&#769;ng tôi. Chu&#769;ng tôi se&#771; tra&#777; l&#417;&#768;i cho quy&#769; kha&#769;ch trong vo&#768;ng 24 gi&#417;&#768;.</FONT></P>', 38, 0, '', 'vn', '', ''),
