(66, '', 'DISCOVERY OF VAN PHONG GULF - VINPEARL LAND', '../products/product_s66.jpg', NULL, 0, '2007-05-13 23:37:35', NULL, 0, 0, NULL, 'WELCOME TO VAN PHONG TOURISM AREA(LARGE ISLAND). YOU COME TO XUAN DUNG BEACH TO HAVE DISCOVER THE STRANGENESSOF NATURE : YOU ONLY USE YOUR HANDS TO DIG A SHORT DISTANCE, YOU CANFIND OUT FREST WATER AT THE SAND ARE NEARBY TO THE SEA.', '<P class=MsoNormal style="TEXT-ALIGN: center" align=center><SPAN lang=FR><FONT face="Georgia, Times New Roman, Times, Serif" color=#0000ff size=5><EM>TOURISM PROGRAM</EM></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="TEXT-ALIGN: center" align=center><SPAN lang=FR><FONT color=#ff00ff size=5>DISCOVERY OF VAN PHONG GULF - VINPEARL LAND</FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="TEXT-ALIGN: center" align=center><SPAN lang=FR><FONT color=#009900 size=3><EM>Duration: 4 days 3 nights</EM></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="TEXT-ALIGN: center" align=center><FONT color=#009900 size=3><EM>Means: by 5 StarsExpress</EM></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify"><FONT color=#ff0000 size=5>DAY 1: HO CHI MINH CITY – NHA TRANG</FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify">-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<FONT color=#0000ff> 05H45’ Dong Khoi travel company’s guider will pick you up at Sai Gon Train Station, take &nbsp; procedures “check in” to the train, have breakfast on train, you will enjoy the best services offered by the 5 Starexpress. </FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify"><FONT color=#0000ff>-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 11h30’ have lunch and rest on train.</FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify"><FONT color=#0000ff>-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 13h30’ come to Nha Trang Train station, you will be picked up by bus to &nbsp;&nbsp; hotel, and then you receive your room and take a rest. </FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify"><FONT color=#0000ff>-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 15h you start visiting and bath by minenral water at Thap Ba – hot mineral water center with services: have a mud-bath, On Tuyen hydrotherapy, hot mineral water. </FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify"><FONT color=#0000ff>-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 17h30&nbsp; you have dinner, walk around the city at night.</FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify"><FONT color=#ff0000 size=4>DAY 2: DISCOVERY OF VAN PHONG GULF</FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify">-<FONT color=#ff00ff> 07h00 you have breakfast, you will be taken by bus to start visiting Van Phong gulf located far 100 km from Nha Trang in the Northern direction, on your way, you will stop taking photographs at Co Don hill (Lonely Hill), enjoy sea view. </FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify"><FONT color=#ff00ff>- 09h00 you come to Dam Mon, go to boats to start discovering the gulf. You will bath and dive to discover corals, multi-color sea fishes with green water at Bai Me. </FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify"><FONT color=#ff00ff>- 11h30 you come to Van Phong tourism area (Large Island) to take bath by fresh water, rest, have lunch, participate to games on sea. </FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify"><FONT color=#ff00ff>- 13h30 you come to Son Dung beach to have contacts with Dang Ha clan – legend has is that they originated from Indonesia; discover the strangeness of nature: you only use your hands to dig a short distance, you can find out fresh water at the sand are nearby to the sea. You are free to bath, rest. </FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify"><FONT color=#ff00ff>- 15h00 boats will take you to learn daily activities of fishermen who breed lobsters, enjoy large rocks that are worn out by sea waves to change into strange shapes. </FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify"><FONT color=#ff00ff>- 16h00 you say goodbye Van Phong gulf to return to Nha Trang, have dinner, walk around the city at night. </FONT></P>\r\n<DIV align=center>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify"><FONT color=#ff00ff></FONT>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<DIV align=center><FONT color=#ff00ff><IMG src="http://222.253.120.101/enver/imagesadv/tour/69258.jpg" width=380></FONT></DIV>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify"><FONT color=#ff0000 size=4>DAY 3: HAVE A TRIP ON HON MUN ISLAND – HON NGOC VIET</FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify">-<FONT color=#6600ff> 07h00 You have breakfast. You will be picked up by bus to Phu Quy port, on your way, you will visit visit Oceanography Institute&nbsp; where keep and protect hundreds of precious fishes of Nha Trang sea. You continue visiting Hon Mun island (Sea swift island) to look at primitive corals and many fish pieces with various splendid colors. </FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify"><FONT color=#6600ff>- 11hh30&nbsp; You come to Tre (Bamboo) Island (Hon Ngoc Viet). You have lunch on island. You visit and take commemorative photographs at Hon Ngoc Viet – tourism-entertainment area (you can participate to some games: water music, legend garden, ferris wheel…you must pay fees), cold drink at Beachcomber Restuarant. You will say goodbye Hon Tre to return to Nha Trang. As you come to Phu Quy port, the bus will take you to the hotel. You have dinner and walk around the city at night. </FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify">&nbsp;<FONT size=4><FONT color=#ff0000>DAY 4: NHA TRANG – HO CHI MINH CITY<B> </B></FONT></FONT></P></DIV>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify">- <FONT color=#0066ff>07h00 you have breakfast, visit Long Son Tu pagoda – the largest Buddhism center in Nha Trang.<BR></FONT>\r\n<DIV align=center><FONT color=#0066ff><IMG src="http://222.253.120.101/enver/imagesa