n Train Station. The program is ended. </P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify">We would like to meet you at next times. </P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify"><B><SPAN lang=FR>Whole package price</SPAN></B></P>\r\n<TABLE class=MsoTableGrid id=table1 style="BORDER-RIGHT: medium none; BORDER-TOP: medium none; FONT-SIZE: 10px; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; BORDER-BOTTOM: medium none; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; BORDER-COLLAPSE: collapse" cellSpacing=0 cellPadding=0 width=297 border=1>\r\n<TBODY>\r\n<TR>\r\n<TD style="BORDER-RIGHT: windowtext 1pt solid; PADDING-RIGHT: 5.4pt; BORDER-TOP: windowtext 1pt solid; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0in; BORDER-LEFT: windowtext 1pt solid; WIDTH: 29px; PADDING-TOP: 0in; BORDER-BOTTOM: windowtext 1pt solid" vAlign=top>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt"><FONT color=#ff0000>Hotel</FONT></SPAN></P></TD>\r\n<TD style="BORDER-RIGHT: windowtext 1pt solid; PADDING-RIGHT: 5.4pt; BORDER-TOP: windowtext 1pt solid; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0in; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; WIDTH: 48px; PADDING-TOP: 0in; BORDER-BOTTOM: windowtext 1pt solid" vAlign=top>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt"><FONT color=#ff0000>02-10K</FONT></SPAN></P></TD>\r\n<TD style="BORDER-RIGHT: windowtext 1pt solid; PADDING-RIGHT: 5.4pt; BORDER-TOP: windowtext 1pt solid; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0in; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; WIDTH: 48px; PADDING-TOP: 0in; BORDER-BOTTOM: windowtext 1pt solid" vAlign=top>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt"><FONT color=#ff0000>10-10K</FONT></SPAN></P></TD>\r\n<TD style="BORDER-RIGHT: windowtext 1pt solid; PADDING-RIGHT: 5.4pt; BORDER-TOP: windowtext 1pt solid; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0in; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; WIDTH: 48px; PADDING-TOP: 0in; BORDER-BOTTOM: windowtext 1pt solid" vAlign=top>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify"><SPAN sty